# Grafana dashboards vendored into the chart at build time (W4-T2b, ADR-0046 §4):
# deploy/observability/dashboards/*.json is the canonical source; this copy is
# produced by deploy/observability/dashboards/sync-to-chart.sh (Helm .Files.Get
# cannot read outside the chart root) and is never committed.
deploy/kubernetes/netops/dashboards/

debug.log
